## User Profile

### Business Rules
- Users can view and update only their own profile (enforced by `req.user.userId`)
- Identity data (name, email) lives in `neon_auth.users`
- Updatable fields: `name`, `avatar_url`, `contact_details`
- Email is read-only (managed by Google — never update email)

```typescript
// src/services/profile.service.ts
async updateProfile(userId: string, updates: ProfileUpdateInput): Promise<UserProfile> {
  // Never allow email update through this endpoint
  const { email, role, isActive, ...safeUpdates } = updates as any;
  return userRepository.updateProfile(userId, safeUpdates);
}
```

